ass=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.16-19?lang=spa#p16\">Doctrina y Convenios 19:16\u201319<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"5.\" id=\"note5\" data-full-marker=\"5.\">\n<p data-aid=\"154474732\" id=\"note5_p1\">Véase <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/138.29-32?lang=spa#p29\">Doctrina y Convenios 138:29\u201332<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"6.\" id=\"note6\" data-full-marker=\"6.\">\n<p data-aid=\"154474734\" id=\"note6_p1\">Véase <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/26.2?lang=spa#p2\">3 Nefi 26:2<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"7.\" id=\"note7\" data-full-marker=\"7.\">\n<p data-aid=\"154474736\" id=\"note7_p1\">Véase <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.8,10-11,14-15?lang=spa#p8\">3 Nefi 11:8, 10\u201311, 14\u201315<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"8.\" id=\"note8\" data-full-marker=\"8.\">\n<p data-aid=\"154474738\" id=\"note8_p1\">Véase <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.4?lang=spa#p4\">3 Nefi 17:4<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"9.\" id=\"note9\" data-full-marker=\"9.\">\n<p data-aid=\"154474740\" id=\"note9_p1\">Véase <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.5?lang=spa#p5\">3 Nefi 17:5<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"10.\" id=\"note10\" data-full-marker=\"10.\">\n<p data-aid=\"154474741\" id=\"note10_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.6?lang=spa#p6\">3 Nefi 17:6<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"11.\" id=\"note11\" data-full-marker=\"11.\">\n<p data-aid=\"154474743\" id=\"note11_p1\">Véase <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/7.11-12?lang=spa#p11\">Alma 7:11\u201312<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-marker=\"12.\" id=\"note12\" data-full-marker=\"12.\">\n<p data-aid=\"154474745\" id=\"note12_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.7?lang=spa#p7\">3 Nefi 17:7<\/a>.<\/p>\n